text: Natasha Marian Obama (born June 10, 2001) is the younger daughter of the 44th president of the United States Barack Obama and Michelle Obama. == Early life == Natasha Marian Obama was born at University of Chicago Medical Center on June 10, 2001, as the younger of two daughters to Barack Obama and Michelle Obama. She was delivered by her parents' friend and physician Anita Blanchard. Her elder sister is Malia Obama. Obama and her sister were named two of "The Most Influential Teens of 2014" by TIME magazine. == Career == Obama made her television debut in a 2008 episode of Access Hollywood. == References == Category:2001 births Category:Living people
title: Sasha Obama
